please note: To play correctly, rename "VCD_PLAY.DAT" to
"VCD_PLAY.EXE" in the videoVCD folder.

This Karaoke CD came with a stand alone player. If you do
not want to use this, simply delete the "VCD_PLAY.DAT" file,
and then edit the "AUTORUN.INF" and delete the line that
references "VCD_PLAY.EXE" file and save. IF you do this,
when you start the CD, you wont see the main menu. But
everything else will play.

This CD looks nicer when played the way it was designed. Either
way, just burn the "VideoVCD" directory onto a blank CD.
